<html
    xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"
    xml:lang="en"
    lang="en"
    metal:use-macro="context/@@main_template/master"
    i18n:domain="launchpad"
>
  <body>

  <div metal:fill-slot="main">

      <div>
        <img alt="" src="/@@/blueprint" />
        <a tal:attributes="href context/fmt:url" tal:content="context/title" />
      </div>

    <div metal:use-macro="context/@@launchpad_form/form">
    </div>

  </div>

  <div metal:fill-slot="help">
    <p>If you have a branch related to a blueprint (implementing
    the feature, or fixing the problem the blueprint outlines),
    you can create a link between them.  The summary field can be used
    to leave a note about the relationship.</p>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
